Install bathroom floor $10 sq.ft. (231x10=2310)

Install shower walls $20 sq.ft. (152x20=3040)

Install shower pan tile $14 sq.ft. (36x14=504)

Install niche $200-300 depending on size (custom made at $275)

Install bench $150

Install schluter strips $20 ea (6x20=120)

Construct new shower pan $40 sq.ft. (36x40=1440)

Plus 1200 materials needed
Plus 200 for schluter strips and grout (1400)

Total 10005.00

