Glass Shower Enclosures

- Sq ft glass cost (3/8” thick) = $40 normal - $45 if notched
- Endurashield + $8 per Sq ft
- Hardware and Brackets included
- Install labor $200 per panel
- Mirror $12.80 per Sq ft
- plus tax

- Data Entries (Square footage, Endurishield footage, panel quantity (un-notched / notched))

